ocr.text: There are 3 ways to peel ginger skin
Squeeze each half of lemon into each jar
Add 2 tbsp. honey into each jar
Add 6 cups of water into a medium pot
Cover and bring it to boil
Turn off stove once the water boils and let stand for 15
This will extract more ginger flavour
or store in refrigerator for cooling
It's so refreshing, healthy and easy to prepare,
I drink it at least twice a week:)
